Token.Abstract: This protocol defines the interface to the upload manager delegate.
Required delegate method that gets called when a background file upload task finishes, successfully or otherwise.

Parameter.Name: manager
Parameter.Abstract: The upload manager instance making the call.

Parameter.Name: file
Parameter.Abstract: The path to the file whose upload task finished or failed.

Parameter.Name: error
Parameter.Abstract: If the upload task failed, this will describe the cause.

Token.Abstract: Optional delegate method available only in debug builds. Called when a background file upload task finishes, successfully or otherwise in debug builds. Provides a URL that can be called for more information about the post-upload status of the data.

Parameter.Name: manager
Parameter.Abstract: The upload manager instance making the call.

Parameter.Name: file
Parameter.Abstract: The path to the file whose upload task finished or failed.

Parameter.Name: url
Parameter.Abstract: The url to call to get more information about the post-upload status of the data.
